TimIQ product goal:
Build a professional payroll and workforce management app with desktop and mobile layouts, role-based access, payroll, time tracking, onboarding, uploads, audit, and system health.

Roles:
- Administrator: global master admin
- Admin: company-scoped admin
- Employee: own data only

Main employee pages:
- Dashboard
- Clock In / Out
- Time Records
- Timesheets
- Week Report
- Pay History
- Starter Form / Onboarding
- Site Progress
- Profile / Change Password

Main management pages:
- Management Overview
- Employees
- Companies
- Workplaces
- Locations
- Site Access
- Payroll Report
- Live Attendance
- Onboarding Review
- Audit Log
- System Health
- Work Progress Admin View

Current completed foundations:
- Auth/login/logout
- Protected routes
- Role-based UI
- Companies
- Company status
- Employees
- Employee edit
- Password reset
- Locations with GPS/geofence
